    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>语法</h1>

<pre><code class="css">[selector]{property:value;}
[selector]{property1:value1;property2:value2;}
[selector1],[selector2]{property:value;}
</code></pre>

<p>例：
<code>css
h1 {color:blue;}
p {color:blue;font-family: "Sans serif";}
h2,h3{color:red;}
</code></p>

<h1>继承</h1>

<p>当前标签没有自己的样式，则继承父标签的样式。</p>

<h1>派生选择器</h1>

<p>根据上下文关系定位元素,已经定义的样式不会被覆盖</p>

<p>html</p>

<p>```</p>

<p><strong></strong></p>


<ul><li><strong></strong></ul>


<pre><code>
css
</code></pre>

<p>li strong{color:red;}
strong{color:blue};
```</p>
